<!doctype html><html lang="ko"><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><title>24개월 건강관리 프로젝트</title>
<style>
:root{color-scheme:dark;--panel:#0b1420;--line:#24475b;--text:#f5f7fa;--muted:#9db0bd;--cyan:#36d8d0;--gold:#e7b74e}*{box-sizing:border-box}body{margin:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#07121b,#030609);color:var(--text);font-family:Arial,"Noto Sans KR",sans-serif}.page{width:min(1180px,100%);margin:auto;padding:22px}header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:18px;padding:18px 0 22px;}.brand{color:var(--cyan);font-size:13px;font-weight:800}h1{margin:7px 0 0;font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,42px)}h2{margin:0 0 14px}h3{color:var(--gold)}p,li{line-height:1.65}.actions{display:flex;gap:8px}.button{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:42px;padding:0 15px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:7px;background:#0b1522;color:var(--text);font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;cursor:pointer}.primary{background:var(--cyan);border-color:var(--cyan);color:#061313}.card{margin-top:14px;padding:20px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:8px;background:rgba(10,19,31,.95)}.hero{padding:28px}.vip-card{border-color:#8a6a28;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(111,75,17,.28),rgba(10,19,31,.97))}.vip-card h2{color:#ffe39b}.benefit-list{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px}.benefit-list span,.status-pill{padding:8px 10px;border:1px solid #526273;border-radius:6px;background:#09111c}.status-pill{color:var(--gold);font-weight:800}.flow{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,minmax(0,1fr));gap:8px}.flow span,.box-item,.metric,.category{padding:13px;border:1px solid #31556a;border-radius:7px;background:#09111c}.grid,.plans,.box,.dashboard{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr));gap:12px}.plan{padding:18px;border:1px solid #31556a;border-radius:7px}.price{font-size:28px;color:var(--gold);font-weight:800}.category-list{columns:3;line-height:1.8}.muted{color:var(--muted)}.notice{border-left:3px solid var(--gold);padding:14px 16px;background:#111018}@media(max-width:850px){.flow,.grid,.plans,.box,.dashboard{grid-template-columns:1fr}.category-list{columns:1}}@media(max-width:620px){.page{padding:12px}header{align-items:stretch;flex-direction:column}.actions,.actions>*{width:100%}}
</style>  <link rel="stylesheet" href="site-navigation.css?v=20260623-fantasy-bg-1">
</head><body><main class="page">
<header><nav class="actions"><a class="button" href="shopping.html">쇼핑하기</a><a class="button" href="index.html">메인 화면</a></nav></header>
<section class="card"><h2>구독 플랜</h2><div class="plans"><div class="plan"><h3>베이직</h3><p class="price">79,000원</p><p>홍채 비교 · 문진 · 리포트</p><button class="button plan-button" data-plan="베이직">이 플랜 기록</button></div><div class="plan"><h3>스탠다드</h3><p class="price">129,000원</p><p>홍채 비교 · 문진 · 리포트 · 건강박스</p><button class="button primary plan-button" data-plan="스탠다드">이 플랜 기록</button></div><div class="plan"><h3>프리미엄</h3><p class="price">199,000원</p><p>건강박스 · 건강도서 · 건강기기 포함</p><button class="button plan-button" data-plan="프리미엄">이 플랜 기록</button></div></div><p id="saveStatus" class="muted"></p></section>
<section id="vip-benefit" class="card vip-card"><h2>보험 VIP 혜택</h2><div id="vipStatus"></div><div id="vipBenefits" class="benefit-list"></div><div id="vipBoxStatus"></div></section>
</main><script src="care-engine.js"></script><script src="subscription.js"></script>  <script src="site-navigation.js?v=20260623-073145"></script>
</body></html>
